{"tid":2144732,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國mainstream media一直附和中共口吻洗白tik tok","createTime":"2020-08-07T17:31:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T19:58:24.000Z","uid":100155,"like":69,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"e0d35a221974888ec155a63d23bebecb249783d2","tid":2144732,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T17:31:38.000Z","msg":"美國mainstream media一直附和中共口吻洗白tik tok<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/BZa0FGThXak\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBZa0FGThXak&d=1Tw5YvH57m5vrKXwbFhC6AKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=88a76b10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/BZa0FGThXak</a><br />\n趕時間可以7:20開始睇，但成條片做得幾好笑<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw佢地2個channel好高質 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/ChinaUncensored\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fc%2FChinaUncensored&d=1Tw5YvH57m5vrKXwbFhC6AKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=78191492\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/c/ChinaUncensored</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/AmericaUncovered\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fc%2FAmericaUncovered&d=1Tw5YvH57m5vrKXwbFhC6AKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=b646a8af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/c/AmericaUncovered</a><br />\n<br />\n不過因為反共反左膠 佢地所有片都被youtube黃標 （views無盈利，同埋難啲出現喺home page）<br />\n<br />\n因為佢主要受眾係美國人，但對中共/左膠嘅認識真係幾一針見血 連香港嘅事都跟得好貼 <br />\n唔同普通鬼佬media，亦唔同垃圾左媒懶係中立咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好值得更多人 尤其美國人睇到 增加佢地對中共嘅認識 令佢地唔好咁天真嬌 同時加強民意<br />\n<br />\n所以希望大家多啲subscribe, cls<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢條片講民主黨權貴點樣陰濕地收俄佬錢 去approve賣核原料比俄國公司<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/fumgTTejLY0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FfumgTTejLY0&d=1Tw5YvH57m5vrKXwbFhC6AKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=2df92c53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/fumgTTejLY0</a><br />\n<br />\n呢條上星期 講港共用疫情藉口延遲選舉 唔比香港人投票<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/OYy3IcviDnY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOYy3IcviDnY&d=1Tw5YvH57m5vrKXwbFhC6AKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=5d879dde\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/OYy3IcviDnY</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fd14a6c93a14ca4835654ddea1e4e71888f1f5e","tid":2144732,"uid":100155,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T17:32:35.000Z","msg":"美總統特朗普：拜登的政策是中國優先，美國最後<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2143187\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2143187</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c1925fb58a04827926d4376349cc00ffc05cf9fc","tid":2144732,"uid":100155,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T17:33:02.000Z","msg":"飲香檳之前，你有一樣野唔記得咗做....<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2144365\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2144365</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4473e4d9ed04811d633efbc1609914f424c0a912","tid":2144732,"uid":307619,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T17:34:07.000Z","msg":"除咗制裁，今日係梓樂離開9個月<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2144688\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2144688</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ccyVKr4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FccyVKr4.png&h=fbc64625&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5tWka9x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5tWka9x.png&h=850fb110&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"33bec330b570f76f7fe1a8dc72998721dc7b5914","tid":2144732,"uid":100155,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T17:35:46.000Z","msg":"德國國會議員：德國及歐盟應該跟隨美國 對中共實施制裁 包括Carrie Lam<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2144621\" da